snippet.title: ONE PIECE World Seeker – TGS Trailer
snippet.description:
Meet Jeanne, leader of the Anti-Navy group, who must work with Luffy to over-throw Isaac, warden of the prison that casts its shadow over all of Jewel Island.

#OnePieceWorldSeeker releases in 2019 for the PS4, X1 & Steam. Pre-order your copy: https://bandainam.co/ONEPIECE
